{"tid":1666700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[the best is yet to come] 水警警長燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-10-21T05:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T19:22:22.000Z","uid":3204,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"626d1dfcb9aa7ec8e54809498e31e9e2e9a63803","tid":1666700,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"【疑因提早退休問題與妻有分歧　水警警長燒炭亡】<br />\n<br />\n今日（10月16日）早上9時許，警方接報指新田新潭路一地盤內，一名男子在私家車內昏迷，救援人員到場後證實男子已氣絕身亡，消息指死者為一名水警。<br />\n<br />\n警方在車內發現燒過的炭，懷疑事主燒炭自殺。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-21-2019/56924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-21-2019%2F56924&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=73ee2be3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-21-2019/56924</a><br />\n<br />\n#水警 #警長 #燒炭"},{"pid":"aad6e72c8972884a58d8c8c27e4e5408cf97b00e","tid":1666700,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"172dd2028fb91452b3f614e06e08020faef54312","tid":1666700,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"根本拖落去一定佢地死，講緊7 8成人支持呀我地"},{"pid":"266ee4089c3e1d5286a0bd97a31ce29362ff3618","tid":1666700,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 21<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>19:00 - 23:00 毋忘721 元朗恐襲三個月靜坐</strong></span><br />\n- 18區黨鐵站大堂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>#39mRunFor721 全港和理跑</strong></span><br />\n- [時間地點不限 跑步計時39分鐘]"},{"pid":"02eabeaad19e9191abf4a715e52180fa588a0418","tid":1666700,"ui